---
source: crates/hid-heusinkveld-protocol/tests/snapshot_encoding.rs
expression: "flags.join(\"\\n\")"
---
0x00: connected=false, calibrated=false, fault=false
0x01: connected=true, calibrated=false, fault=false
0x02: connected=false, calibrated=true, fault=false
0x03: connected=true, calibrated=true, fault=false
0x04: connected=false, calibrated=false, fault=true
0x05: connected=true, calibrated=false, fault=true
0x06: connected=false, calibrated=true, fault=true
0x07: connected=true, calibrated=true, fault=true
